snippet.title: Longplay of Skies of Arcadia Legends (1/3)
snippet.description:
Longplay of Skies of Arcadia Legends, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Jan. 27th, 2003. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
